<div align="center"><span class="textbold_orange">ERK Phosphorylation Status Screening Service (Code: pERK Service)</span><br /><br /></div>

<span class="textbold_orange">Summary</span><br />
Using our <a href="/ERK-Phosphorylation-Assay-Kit" target="_blank">EnzyFluo&trade; ERK Phosphorylation Assay Kit</a>, we screen for modulators that increase or decrease ERK phosphorylation status in cells. We measure the ERK phosphorylation kinetics, EC50, and IC50 of cells treated with modulators. Testing can be run on a wide variety of cell lines.
<br />
<br />
